            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/lmd/campain/svalbard-global-seed-vault/news/20000-new-seed-samples-deposited-in-sval.html?id=751916" title="">
                        20,000 new seed samples deposited in Svalbard</a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[27.02.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    A new shipment of seeds from food plants has been deposited in the Svalbard Global Seed Vault for long-term storage. The shipment, that was transported to the seed vault in Longyearbyen this week, contains 20,000 seed samples from Japan, Brazil, Peru, Mexico and the USA.</p>
                
                
                
                
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr class="seperator" />
    
        <div class="ArticleView">
            <a href="/en/dep/lmd/campain/svalbard-global-seed-vault/news/norwegian-contribution-to-the-internatio.html?id=750481" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/imgpreviews/00/00/03/78/37821_img___1391681445.jpg" alt="Statssekretær i Landbruks- og matdepartementet Hanne Maren Blåfjelldal" title="Statssekretær i Landbruks- og matdepartementet Hanne Maren Blåfjelldal" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/lmd/campain/svalbard-global-seed-vault/news/norwegian-contribution-to-the-internatio.html?id=750481" title="">
                        Norwegian contribution to the International Treaty on Plant Genetic Resources for Food and Agriculture's Benefit-Sharing Fund</a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[06.02.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    Norway is paying close to NOK 700,000 to the International Plant Treaty's Benefit-Sharing Fund. This corresponds to 0.1 per cent of the value of the trade in seed products in agriculture in Norway in 2013, and is an annual contribution from Norwegian agriculture toward the efforts of farmers in developing countries to safeguard plant diversity.  </p>
                
                
                
                
            </div>
